---
title: "withdraw (AuctionBidder)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_guard: onlyRole(DEFAULT_ADMIN_ROLE)
    q_guard --> q_validate: to == address(0)
    q_validate --> q_revert: true
    q_validate --> q_iter: false
    q_revert --> [*]: revert InvalidZeroAddress()
    q_iter --> q_transfer: i < assetAmounts.length
    q_iter --> q_final: i >= assetAmounts.length
    q_transfer --> q_iter: safeTransfer(to, assetAmounts[i].amount); i++
    q_final --> [*]

    note right of q_iter
        INV-001: All asset transfers go to the same destination address
        INV-002: Loop processes every AssetAmount entry without early exit
        INV-003: safeTransfer reverts on failure, ensuring atomicity
    end note
